[
  {
    "user": "UC2A2ARPT",
    "type": "message",
    "ts": "1765076969.079719",
    "client_msg_id": "3d467cd6-fec9-4d46-925c-26fb6b70af9a",
    "text": "I've been doing a <https://eli.li/december-adventure|December Adventure>, which is a lovely little thing initiated by <@UMQ6LR9NZ>. I should have mentioned this a week ago, but like… it's never too late to hop on board! The gist of it is… well, actually, here's how _I personally interpret it, even though this is at odds with the \"official\" post_::::\n\nYou should do a weird little extra thing every day. Something you don't normally do. Maybe it's creative. Maybe it's coding. Doesn't matter. But try to find a space moment in your day to do a weird little extra thing.\n\nTry not to feel any pangs if you miss a day. Don't dread it. Just look for an opportunity to try something out.\n\nAnd, if the spirit moves you, post about it somewhere. Maybe on your personal website — I've been posting my <https://ivanish.ca/december-adventure/|december adventures> on my personal website, natch. But a lot of folks (and there are, in fact, quite a few folks doing this now, which is truly humbling) post on Mastodon about it. Or you could just post here in <#C03RR0W5DGC|>. That'd be great.\n\nIf you're doing a December Adventure, let me know!",
    "team": "T5TCAFTA9",
    "thread_ts": "1765076969.079719",
    "reply_count": 4,
    "reply_users_count": 2,
    "latest_reply": "1765077821.651959",
    "reply_users": [
      "UC2A2ARPT",
      "UMQ6LR9NZ"
    ],
    "is_locked": false,
    "subscribed": false,
    "blocks": [
      {
        "type": "rich_text",
        "block_id": "q0mCG",
        "elements": [
          {
            "type": "rich_text_section",
            "elements": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I've been doing a "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://eli.li/december-adventure",
                "text": "December Adventure"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ", which is a lovely little thing initiated by "
              },
              {
                "type": "user",
                "user_id": "UMQ6LR9NZ"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ". I should have mentioned this a week ago, but like… it's never too late to hop on board! The gist of it is… well, actually, here's how "
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "I personally interpret it, even though this is at odds with the \"official\" post",
                "style": {
                  "italic": true
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "::::\n\nYou should do a weird little extra thing every day. Something you don't normally do. Maybe it's creative. Maybe it's coding. Doesn't matter. But try to find a space moment in your day to do a weird little extra thing.\n\nTry not to feel any pangs if you miss a day. Don't dread it. Just look for an opportunity to try something out.\n\nAnd, if the spirit moves you, post about it somewhere. Maybe on your personal website — I've been posting my "
              },
              {
                "type": "link",
                "url": "https://ivanish.ca/december-adventure/",
                "text": "december adventures"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " on my personal website, natch. But a lot of folks (and there are, in fact, quite a few folks doing this now, which is truly humbling) post on Mastodon about it. Or you could just post here in "
              },
              {
                "type": "channel",
                "channel_id": "C03RR0W5DGC"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": ". That'd be great.\n\nIf you're doing a December Adventure, let me know!"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ],
