                "text": ". It's sad to look back at 30 years of working in computational science and noting that my (almost) first environment, APL, was the best I ever had in terms of being made for the work I do.\n\n\"Almost\" because my very first programming environment was BASIC on a TRS-80. I learned APL (initially on an IBM mainframe) a year later."
              }
